    <title>hexo + github action自动部署</title>
    <link href="https://lidiudiudiu.github.io/blog/2025/04/28/hexo-github-action%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/"/>
    <id>https://lidiudiudiu.github.io/blog/2025/04/28/hexo-github-action%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2/</id>
    <published>2025-04-28T12:14:00.000Z</published>
