    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="hexo框架-github-action自动化部署"><a href="#hexo框架-github-action自动化部署" class="headerlink" title="hexo框架 + github action自动化部署"></a>hexo框架 + github action自动化部署</h3><h4 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h4><p><strong>首先安装nodejs git 这里不说了自己网上找教程  nodejs 18版本</strong></p><ol><li>Git是一个免费的、开源的版本控制软件。在Windows上安装git，一般为msysgit，<br>官方下载地址 :<a href="http://code.google.com/p/msysgit/downloads/list">http://code.google.com/p/msysgit/downloads/list</a><br>安装步骤下一步即可…</li><li>nodejs官网：<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">https://nodejs.org/en/</a></li></ol><p>判断是否安好</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v </span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br><span class="line">git --version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="安装hexo"><a href="#安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="安装hexo"></a>安装hexo</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli  //hexo安装</span><br><span class="line">hexo init</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426195517488.png" alt="image-20250426195517488"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426195555502.png" alt="image-20250426195555502"></p><p>如上可以看到已经初步看到页面</p><hr><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init </span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &#x27;初始化&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426195900106.png" alt="image-20250426195900106"></p><p>把marster分支改成main</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426200312483.png" alt="image-20250426200312483"></p><p>使用pure主题 <a href="https://github.com/cofess/hexo-theme-pure">https://github.com/cofess/hexo-theme-pure</a></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426200526881.png" alt="image-20250426200526881"></p><p>根目录下新建__config.pure.yml 配置文件 将原有主题内容复制过去_</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426200834079.png" alt="image-20250426200834079"></p><p>同理将pure下的__source中的内容复制到根目录的source里_,并新建一个image文件夹 放两张图片 一个是图片 一个是网站icon图标</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426201450917.png" alt="image-20250426201450917"></p><p>主题配置文件下</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426202055142.png" alt="image-20250426202055142"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426202152441.png" alt="image-20250426202152441"></p><p>favicon改了 avatar改了 </p><p>站点配置文件下 language改了 theme改成pure</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426202324376.png" alt="image-20250426202324376"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426202635907.png" alt="image-20250426202635907"></p><p>安装一系列需要的插件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-wordcount --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-json-content --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-sitemap --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-baidu-sitemap --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>页面大概如下</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250426202745679.png" alt="image-20250426202745679"></p><h4 id="部署到github上"><a href="#部署到github上" class="headerlink" title="部署到github上"></a>部署到github上</h4><p>参考这篇文章 <a href="https://xulianjun.github.io/2024/09/08/Hexo%20+%20GitHub%20Action%EF%BC%8C%E9%9B%B6%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%96%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/">https://xulianjun.github.io/2024/09/08/Hexo%20+%20GitHub%20Action%EF%BC%8C%E9%9B%B6%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E5%8C%96%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</a></p><ol><li>创建仓库</li></ol><p>建一个私有仓库</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250428105948901.png" alt="image-20250428105948901"></p><p>再建一个公有仓库</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250428110042429.png" alt="image-20250428110042429"></p><ol start="2"><li><p>创建token </p><p>点击右上角头像 ——&gt; settings -&gt; developer  settings -&gt; <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250428110341680.png" alt="image-20250428110341680"></p></li></ol><p>创建token </p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250428110556964.png" alt="image-20250428110556964"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250428111838350.png" alt="image-20250428111838350"></p><p>token添加到公有仓库</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250428112416901.png" alt="image-20250428112416901"></p><p>下一步</p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250428112022113.png" alt="image-20250428112022113"></p><p>注意用户名要小写</p><p>然后配置工作流 </p><p>在根目录下的.github文件夹下新建workflows文件下新建deploy.yml文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">name: Deploy Hexo to GitHub Pages</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">on:</span><br><span class="line">  push:</span><br><span class="line">    branches:</span><br><span class="line">      - main  # 当推送到 main 分支时触发</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">jobs:</span><br><span class="line">  build:</span><br><span class="line">    runs-on: ubuntu-latest</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    steps:</span><br><span class="line">      - name: Checkout repository</span><br><span class="line">        uses: actions/checkout@v4  # 升级到 v4 并启用子模块</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      - name: Setup Node.js</span><br><span class="line">        uses: actions/setup-node@v2</span><br><span class="line">        with:</span><br><span class="line">          node-version: &#x27;v18.20.7&#x27; #这里版本需要注意</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      - name: Clone theme</span><br><span class="line">        run: |</span><br><span class="line">          git clone https://github.com/cofess/hexo-theme-pure.git themes/pure</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      - name: Clean Cache</span><br><span class="line">        run: |</span><br><span class="line">          rm -rf node_modules</span><br><span class="line">          rm -rf public</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      - name: Install Dependencies</span><br><span class="line">        run: |</span><br><span class="line">              npm install</span><br><span class="line">              npm install hexo-renderer-pug hexo-renderer-stylus --save</span><br><span class="line">              npm install hexo-wordcount --save</span><br><span class="line">              npm install hexo-generator-json-content --save</span><br><span class="line">              npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span><br><span class="line">              npm install hexo-generator-sitemap --save</span><br><span class="line">              npm install hexo-generator-baidu-sitemap --save  #pure主题对应插件</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      - name: Install Hexo Git Deployer</span><br><span class="line">        run: |</span><br><span class="line">          npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line">          npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      - name: Clean and Generate Static Files</span><br><span class="line">        run: |</span><br><span class="line">          hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">          hexo generate</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      - name: Configure Git</span><br><span class="line">        run: |</span><br><span class="line">          git config --global user.name &#x27;github-actions[bot]&#x27;</span><br><span class="line">          git config --global user.email &#x27;github-actions[bot]@users.noreply.github.com&#x27;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      - name: Deploy to GitHub Pages</span><br><span class="line">        run: |</span><br><span class="line">          cd public/</span><br><span class="line">          git init</span><br><span class="line">          git add -A</span><br><span class="line">          git commit -m &quot;Create by workflows&quot;</span><br><span class="line">          git branch -M main</span><br><span class="line">          git remote add origin https://&#123;token&#125;@github.com/lidiudiudiu/blog.git    # 保存静态网页文件的公开仓 token注意换</span><br><span class="line">          git push origin HEAD:main -f</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>代码上传到源码仓库等待工作流安装完成注意本地为main分支</p><p>在展示仓库里setting&gt;page里 </p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250428115003864.png" alt="image-20250428115003864"></p><p>等待3 5分钟网站出现</p><p>网站出现后没有样式 </p><ol><li><p>用户名没有小写</p></li><li><p><em>config.yml里配置root和url</em></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Lidiudiudiu/image-bed/main/image-20250428120203285.png" alt="image-20250428120203285"></p><p>重新push提交看效果</p></li></ol><p>搭建完成</p><p>想看视频教程推荐这个 <a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1fNNreEEDi/?spm_id_from=333.1007.top_right_bar_window_history.content.click&vd_source=ac554fa267c1192e89cf158e9825bc55">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1fNNreEEDi/?spm_id_from=333.1007.top_right_bar_window_history.content.click&amp;vd_source=ac554fa267c1192e89cf158e9825bc55</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
